{"tid":1712444,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中大圍城只能有三個可能結局","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:08:11.000Z","uid":40478,"like":279,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f9651b469d74603bb1903f6013411a743a58ce","tid":1712444,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"一係64屠城，殺哂所有人，但中國顯然係承受唔起呢個代價，如果敢，一開始就應該出坦克車而唔係水炮車<br />\n<br />\n二係捉哂所有人告暴動，呢個對object係最好既解決方法，問題係攻左成日都入唔到去，顯然係唔升級武力下係做唔到，但升級武力就會變成結局一<br />\n<br />\n三係對Object最差既選擇，就係先撤退再事後清算，問題係就算事後捉幾多人都好，object能夠承受係正面戰鬥被擊退既威望損失嗎？林鄭都講明，佢只有三萬黑警，呢家既香港本來係無法管治，如果連object既威懾力都無左，偽香港政府就乜都無哂<br />\n<br />\n如果一開始無屠城既決心，根本唔應該攻城，呢家全香港、全中共都要陪班無腦物件一齊進退兩難，落命令果件物件睇怕事後都要死全家先得了"},{"pid":"3d01cbd0604b06378508907921fcf0406106aa25","tid":1712444,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n（twitter 突發）美國參議員Hawley 為警察攻入中大校園出聲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"805d43048d47fc8a351ef29ce93e0d9f2cd7b015","tid":1712444,"uid":121869,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"我想講一講既係防暴分區唔係用18區<br />\n而係港島、東九、西九、新界南、新界北<br />\n<br />\n暴大所在既沙田, 屬於新界南<br />\n如果想用區暴動去救佢的話<br />\n可以吹雞 荃+葵+青+東涌+沙+馬+火炭呢啲集中暴動<br />\n拉對角線最長距離去打<br />\n<br />\n其他區保持有零散開花去迫佢留住兵力<br />\n<br />\n而家集中晒沙田大埔<br />\n沙田屬新界南<br />\n大埔屬新界北<br />\n只會被兩區輕取....<br />\n就算十八區開花要開得有智慧<br />\n//<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC%2F&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7QfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=664f9a04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC/</a>"},{"pid":"fbf7ebef07366f4a66e848b5f4919e64d18aa3d4","tid":1712444,"uid":147916,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"屌有次有個fd醉咗喺地鐵入面痾尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開車啲尿就流嚟流去，搞到啲人下個站即刻落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起都覺得區心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeb36d79d570d4f4e59848f3b23d7a6e6326c63","tid":1712444,"uid":40478,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"物件居然撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來真係蠢唔係扮"},{"pid":"4bf8b78da7e00e1ea425436ff7a0be946ebb82b7","tid":1712444,"uid":76310,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"肯定會再攻"},{"pid":"6d69e73c70e12c98a0cb53f7578bc32e945a6f46","tid":1712444,"uid":172031,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5aeb36d79d570d4f4e59848f3b23d7a6e6326c63","tid":1712444,"uid":40478,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"物件居然撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來真係蠢唔係扮"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c680d64dcb4b8b701b30ee1286dbd5ad0494b13","tid":1712444,"uid":299694,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6d69e73c70e12c98a0cb53f7578bc32e945a6f46","tid":1712444,"uid":172031,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5aeb36d79d570d4f4e59848f3b23d7a6e6326c63","tid":1712444,"uid":40478,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"物件居然撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來真係蠢唔係扮"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"中大人已經預左死，黑狗有呢個心理準備？"},{"pid":"257274a766997e7d35de63a0e059b954f045691a","tid":1712444,"uid":267277,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"第四，黑狗扮撒退